s are seeking out third spaces and membership clubs surrounding wellness, to improve their health while also socializing.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108273563-1772642112048-neutral_pool_1.jpg?v=1772642209&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"Pharma & Health Policy","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108272927","title":"2 confidence-building tools for parents to set kids up for 'a lifetime of success,' from a mental performance coach","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T18:49:21.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/confidence-building-tools-parents-help-kids-succeed.html","description":"Parents who prioritize boosting their kids' confidence are \"setting them up for a lifetime of success,\" says mental performance coach Cindra Kamphoff.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108275070-1772834938957-gettyimages-994522096-wpef00357.jpeg?v=1772835017&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108275068","title":"FDA vaccine head will step down in April after string of controversial decisions","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T18:04:07.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/06/fda-vaccine-head-prasad-step-down.html","description":"Vinay Prasad is leaving his post as director of the Center for Biologics Evaluation and Research.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108135341-1745412209860-gettyimages-2210921684-AA_23042025_2190266.jpeg?v=1772838654&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"Pharma & Health Policy","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-NYT Economy-https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/business/economy/health-care-hiring-labor-market.html","title":"Health Care Has Become the Lifeblood of the Labor Market","source":"NYT Economy","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T17:59:18.000Z","url":"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/business/economy/health-care-hiring-labor-market.html","description":"An aging population is drawing workers to medical and social care, creating reliable jobs and revealing weakness for the rest of the economy.","imageUrl":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/02/24/multimedia/00biz-healthcare-jobs-wcvh/00biz-healthcare-jobs-wcvh-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg","theme":"Employment & Labor","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108273784","title":"Iran war could make affordability bigger issue in 2026 elections","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T17:27:55.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/iran-war-affordability-midterm.html","description":"The 2026 midterm election will determine whether Democrats can win back majorities in both chambers of Congress, and check President Donald Trump's policies.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108239748-17653738902025-12-10t002055z_1024944128_rc2bdialu907_rtrmadp_0_usa-trump.jpeg?v=1765373907&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"US"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108273046","title":"Iran war threatens $11.7 trillion global travel industry as passengers get caught in crossfire","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T15:56:05.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/05/iran-war-travel-flights-cruise-hotels.html","description":"Travelers who are far from falling missiles, drone attacks and other geopolitical flashpoints aren't immune to ripple effects.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108273790-1772653707753-gettyimages-2263967601-AFP_99P866E.jpeg?v=1772653797&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Global"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274951","title":"Trump admin announces $20 billion reinsurance program for oil tankers during Iran war","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T15:33:31.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/06/trump-reinsurance-oil-iran-war.html","description":"Tanker traffic through the Strait of Hormuz remains at a standstill as the Iran war engulfs the region.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108274228-1772723263687-gettyimages-2264255797-AFP_99ZD7VD.jpeg?v=1772823786&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274759","title":"Here are 3 themes that drove another challenging week on Wall Street","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T15:29:52.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/here-are-3-themes-that-drove-another-challenging-week-on-wall-street.html","description":"Surprising economic data, another batch of earnings, and an intensifying conflict in the Middle East all combined to move the market, mostly downward.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108274882-17728175032026-03-06t171619z_706146746_rc21zja0hmdp_rtrmadp_0_usa-stocks.jpeg?v=1772817626&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"US"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108269889","title":"Middle-income homebuyers have $30,000 more buying power than a year ago, research finds. It's still not enough","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T14:30:02.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/median-income-households-buying-power.html","description":"While the amount that a median-income household can afford is higher than it was a year ago, it is still below the median price for a single-family home.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/107053767-1651251933744-gettyimages-1329584004-pam_2940copy.jpeg?v=1772052458&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108268508","title":"When to talk to AI chatbots about mental health—and when to stay far away, professionals say","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T14:05:01.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/when-you-shouldand-shouldntuse-chatgpt-as-a-therapist-from-experts.html","description":"Some Americans are using AI chatbots for therapy. Mental health experts share when it is, and isn't, safe to use those tools for emotional support.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108272388-1772490885560-gettyimages-2161537480-dsc04397.jpeg?v=1772490941&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"AI Industry Disruption","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108275098","title":"Berkshire CEO Greg Abel on working with Buffett, Kraft Heinz and using all his salary to buy the stock","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T13:31:42.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/berkshire-ceo-greg-abel-on-working-with-buffett-kraft-heinz-and-using-all-his-salary-to-buy-the-stock.html","description":"Berkshire Hathaway's new CEO, Greg Abel, generated some significant headlines during a roughly half-hour live interview on CNBC's \"Squawk Box.\"","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108274137-1772716073261-SG-Abel-02.jpg?v=1772716146&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108275106","title":"Iran's internet blackout extends into second week: NetBlocks","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T13:05:42.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/irans-internet-blackout-extends-into-second-week-netblocks.html","description":"Iran's government cut internet connectivity shortly after start of U.S.-Israeli attacks on Feb. 28.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/102244480-internet-cafe-iran.jpg?v=1529451536&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274331","title":"How China is challenging the U.S. to become the next great space power ","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T13:00:01.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/07/china-us-space-race-rockets.html","description":"A new report warns that the U.S. could lose its dominance in space to China in the next few years.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/106880289-1620535066811-gettyimages-1315232701-vcg111327814732.jpeg?v=1772818091&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Emerging","emerging_label":"","region":"China"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108275013","title":"Trump says 