w3v8o#0","title":"There’s an inflation wave coming - what does the Iran war mean for the UK economy?","source":"BBC Business","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T04:02:08.000Z","url":"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/cd9gvv5w3v8o?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss","description":"Economic consequences are an intrinsic aspect of the Iran conflict, writes BBC economics editor Faisal Islam.","imageUrl":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/0c30/live/fa05f930-19b0-11f1-b9ec-35cf11968638.jpg","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"EU"},{"id":"rss-NYT Economy-https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/business/economy/jobs-report-unemployment-democrats-republicans-midterms.html","title":"Democrats Blame Trump For Jobs Report as Republicans Play Defense","source":"NYT Economy","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T00:11:34.000Z","url":"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/06/business/economy/jobs-report-unemployment-democrats-republicans-midterms.html","description":"The weaker-than-expected numbers quickly became a source of tension between the two parties ahead of the midterm elections.","imageUrl":"https://static01.nyt.com/images/2026/03/06/multimedia/06biz-jobs-report-politics-Schumer-bvtk/06biz-jobs-report-politics-Schumer-bvtk-mediumSquareAt3X.jpg","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274995","title":"Palantir rallies 15% for the week as Iran war boosts prospects, muting Anthropic concern","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-07T00:07:18.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/06/palantir-stock-jumps-15percent-in-week-on-iran-war-boosts-anthropic-muted.html","description":"Palantir's stock had its best week since August and outperformed all of its large-cap tech peers after the U.S. attacked Iran.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108254383-1770070558669-108254383-17689273942026-01-20t140915z_1241214190_rc225ja1zdei_rtrmadp_0_davos-meeting.jpeg?v=1772841072&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Other"},