-Israeli strikes on Iran over the weekend gave way to a week with topsy-turvy markets, spiking mortgage rates and higher prices at the pump.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108272325-1772486864550-gettyimages-2264441115-6e6a2683_copy_67u8ptai.jpeg?v=1772743608&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Credit & Banking","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274719","title":"U.S. payrolls unexpectedly fell by 92,000 in February; unemployment rate rises to 4.4%","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-06T16:12:55.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/06/february-2026-jobs-report.html","description":"Nonfarm payrolls were expected to increase 50,000 in February while the unemployment rate held steady at 4.3%.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108195133-1757104928644-gettyimages-2233904215-_73a2771_gqeshet9.jpeg?v=1757104967&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Employment & Labor","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-CNBC-108274788","title":"Analysis: Tough jobs report puts Trump's Iran war plans to the test","source":"CNBC","publishedAt":"2026-03-06T16:12:54.000Z","url":"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/06/jobs-report-trump-iran-israel-war-economy.html","description":"The economy is showing signs of slowing as the Iran war quickly pushes up gas prices.","imageUrl":"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108270145-17720569322026-02-25t220047z_1680138003_rc29tjapxdzz_rtrmadp_0_usa-trump.jpeg?v=1772056963&amp;w=1920&amp;h=1080","theme":"Geopolitics & Conflicts","region":"Other"},{"id":"rss-BBC Business-https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c14m57k8vgeo#0","title":"Surge in jet fuel prices could push up air fares, analysts warn","source":"BBC Business","publishedAt":"2026-03-06T15:51:05.000Z","url":"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c14m57k8vgeo?at_medium=RSS&at_campaign=rss","description":"Disruption to supplies from the Gulf due to the Middle East conflict has pushed the cost up by more than 80%.","imageUrl":"https://ichef.bbci.co.uk/ace/standard/240/cpsprodpb/851e/